 the PP includes links to third party privacy policies, usually when it states that any engagement with third parties will be governed by third party privacy policies", "type": "singleselect", "values": [{"label": "[ 0 ] - no", "value": "0"}, {"label": "[ 1 ] - yes", "value": "1"}, {"label": "[ . ] - n/a (in cases where there are no relationships with third parties of any sort)", "value": "."}], "details": "please select the most appropriate option", "opp_info": "", "question": "Sharing - 3rd Parties", "ccpa_info": "", "gdpr_info": "", "threshold": "", "identifier": "v29_2020", "values_raw": "0,1,."}, {"": "", "info": "What is consent mechanism for sharing/selling PII or sensitive information to entities that aren't service providers (except for the purpose of effecting, administering, or enforcing a transaction, sending future correspondence to user, research, internal database compilation, servicing website)?", "type": "multiselect", "values": [{"label": "[ 0 ] - mandatory or does not disclose", "value": "0"}, {"label": "[ 1 ] - opt-out  [The default is for the user to share PII with third parties, but the PP gives the user the opportunity to opt out]", "value": "1"}, {"label": "[ 2 ] - opt-in [User must consent before data can be shared with or collected/used by third party]", "value": "2"}, {"label": "[ . ] - N/A (applicable if firm does not engage in this practice)", "value": "."}], "details": "", "opp_info": "", "question": "Sharing - Consent", "ccpa_info": "", "gdpr_info": "", "threshold": "", "identifier": "v31_2020", "values_raw": "0,1,2,."}, {"": "", "info": "PP has a Change of Terms (COT) provision that explicitly or implicitly allows entity to change agreement?", "type": "singleselect", "values": [{"label": "[ 0 ] - no", "value": "0"}, {"label": "[ 1 ] - yes", "value": "1"}], "details": "please select the most appropriate option", "opp_info": "", "question": "Notice - Change of Terms", "ccpa_info": "", "gdpr_info": "", "threshold": "", "identifier": "v32